name: www.Jobbam.com
tag_list: free-resume-post, resume, job, find-job-online, resume-search-engine, free-resume, online-resume, online-jobs
overview:
Jobbam.com is a free resume search engine. It is a place where jobseekers go to post their resume for free to be discovered by prospective employers.

Jobbam.com also gives users the necessary tools to market their resume effectively to increase their chances of finding work.

Jobbam.com allows users to access and update their resume from anywhere at anytime, and search engine optimizes their resumes in major search engines. This gives a jobbam.com user an advantage over a competitor because their resume will be viewed by more employers.
